<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>سُورَةُ الْوَاقِعَة<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>تَفْسِيرُ السُّورَة<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{إِذَا وَقَعَتِ الْوَاقِعَةُ , لَيْسَ لِوَقْعَتِهَا كَاذِبَةٌ , خَافِضَةٌ رَافِعَةٌ , إِذَا رُجَّتِ الْأَرْضُ رَجًّا , وَبُسَّتِ الْجِبَالُ بَسًّا}</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٤٦:</span> <span class="c3">{خَافِضَةٌ}</span>: لِقَوْمٍ إِلَى النَّارِ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c3">{رَافِعَةٌ}</span>: إِلَى الجَنَّةِ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ مُجَاهِدٌ:</span> <span class="c3">{رُجَّتْ}</span>: زُلْزِلَتْ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c3">{بُسَّتْ}</span>: فُتَّتْ , لُتَّتْ , كَمَا يُلَتُّ السَّوِيقُ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) [الواقعة: ١ - ٥]</p> </div>